Package org.emath.model.communication

Class Summary
Backup This class is used to map the old state of content to the backup table when it is updates.
ClientBook This class holds only information that the client may need to know about an e-book.
Course This class represents a single course.
CourseLock This class is used to prevent changes to a single course while a transaction is in progress.
DummySystemUpdate This class is used to create updates to dummy books.
Exam This class represents an exam, that students can take.
ExamAccess This class is used to manage who can access exams.
ExamSolution These are the answers to an exam by a user.
History This class is used to track the session history of a user.
LogEntry Represents a error log entry.
LoginAttempt This class is used to return information to the client about login attempts that failed.
School This class represents a single school.
SystemUpdate This class represents an update to the book framework and is not content related.
TrafficLogEntry This class is used to log all traffic between the client and the server.
User This class represents a user instance.
